                              "type": "script",
                              "code": "\trows = BlueRidge.Common.Util.extractQualifiedValues(value) or []\n\topts = BlueRidge.Common.Util.extractQualifiedValues(self.view.custom.fieldOptions) or []\n\tout = []\n\tfor i, r in enumerate(rows):\n\t\tr = dict(r or {})\n\t\tr['rowIndex'] = i\n\t\tout.append({'row': r, 'fieldOptions': opts})\n\treturn out"
